comments: Anthony (POR) cleanly dislodges the ball from Bazley (OKC) during his drive.
Kanter (POR) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Bazley (OKC) and absorbs the contact.
Roby (OKC) makes incidental contact to Anthony's (POR) arm after the release of his driving shot attempt.
Dort (OKC) makes incidental contact to Kanter's (OKC) body during the rebound.
Williams (OKC) dislodges Lillard (POR) from his position during the rebound.
Lillard (POR) jumps vertically and absorbs the body contact from Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) and the contact with his arm is marginal.
Kanter (POR) makes incidental contact to Roby's (OKC) arm during the rebound.
Simons (POR) makes marginal contact with Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) body at the end of his drive as he moves along his path.
Lillard (POR) releases from Dort (OKC) on the perimeter.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) blocks the shot attempt by Simons (POR) before making marginal contact with his arm.
Roby (OKC) makes marginal contact to Kanter's (POR) body during his shooting motion on his shot attempt near the basket.
Lillard (POR) commits a take foul on Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC).
Williams (OKC) makes incidental contact to Lillard's (POR) foot during the inbounds.
Roby (OKC) slightly extends his arm into Kanter (POR) but does not dislodge him during the rebound.
Kanter (POR) briefly grasps Roby's (OKC) arm off ball.
Replay review of the shooting foul called on Dort (OKC) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed successful.  Dort reaches in and makes clean contact with the ball while defending Lillard (POR).
Anthony (POR) makes marginal contact with Roby's (OKC) arm that he moves through to tip the jump ball.
Trent Jr. (POR) commits a take foul on Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC).
Lillard (POR) cleanly deflects the loose ball from Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) during the rebound.
Lillard (POR) releases from Dort (OKC) prior to gathering the ball on the perimeter.
Kanter (POR) commits a take foul on Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC).
Little (POR) briefly places his forearm to Dort's (OKC) front during the inbound.
Lillard (POR) commits a take foul on Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC).
A timeout is granted to OKC as Roby (OKC) makes incidental contact with Lillard (POR) during the inbound.
